ed their examples with the use of splash guards in addition to PPE.<\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">After inactivation, samples should be refrigerated or stored on ice before same-day processing through the assay.<\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><span>On our <\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/floodlamp.bio\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">website<\/span><\/a><span> are our protocols in worksheet form as we use in the lab. This and more information will be live soon.<\/span><\/div><\/div>","changed_on":1599633483}